reviews.text: the latest branch of the brand, always my first choice in hk for a cuppa. serious coffee with window walls looking to a nice park full of trees. friendly and attentive service. dogs-friendly.
Proper food and coffee. Was not disappointed
Very good dripped coffee!
So lovely. My favorite outpost. Flat white with oat milk was consistently delicious

A very bright and clean tasting coffee at a perfect temperature. A light sweetness at the beginning and a mild nutty aftertaste.
Highly rate this one at 8/10.

With the health benefits of turmeric this oat milk latte is a nice way to Jaz up up your morning breakfast. Delicately smooth and was better than expected.
